high_descs: turn left and then turn right immediately passing the counter on the right, move forward towards the toaster on the counter and turn right moving to the counter to the left of the stove
pick up the knife off of the counter
turn to the right and move forward towards the counter with the plate on it
put the knife on to the plate
pick up the plate with the knife on it
turn around and move to the sink
put the plate with the knife on it in to the sink
anns.task_desc: put a plate and knife stack in to the sink

high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the door, take a right just past the fridge and walk to the stove ahead.
Pick up the silver knife to the left of the stove on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the counter with the black plate.
Put the knife on the black plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate with the knife from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink ahead.
Put the plate with the knife inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a knife in a sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and right, then right again to find the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter, to the left of the stove.
Carry the knife and turn turn to the right to the other counter.
Place the knife in a pan in the middle of the counter.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Carry the pan and turn around to find the sink.
Place the pan and knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan and knife to the sink.
